[src:rna-interference/microrna] This paves the way for possible genetic obesity treatments.
[src:rna-interference/microrna] Another class of miRNAs that regulate insulin resistance, obesity, and diabetes, is the let-7 family.
[src:rna-interference/microrna] Let-7 accumulates in human tissues during the course of aging.
